comments: Recorded live at Musikhalle in Hamburg, Germany. First recorded by Fitzgerald as part of her live concert at Juan-Les-Pins in Antibes on the Cote d’Azure in July 1964. This version did not appear on the original LP release of that concert. It was first released on the Japanese CD reissue in 1989 on Verve J25J 25147.
